.PP
Configuration layers (lowest to highest precedence):
.PP
Defaults \(-> /etc/.muxmrc \(-> ~/.muxmrc \(-> ./.muxmrc \(-> \-\-profile \(-> CLI flags
.PP
.B muxm
requires
.B bash 4.3
or later. macOS ships bash\ 3.2; install a modern version
(e.g.,
